ResonantChain.AttributesDescription: Casting Mid-air Attack Cloudburst Dance enhances Rover's resistance to interruption for 3s.

Casting Resonance Skill Unbound Flow continuously restores HP for the Resonator on the field by 20% of Rover's ATK every 3s for 30s. When the Resonator on the field has an HP lower than 35%, immediately restore 10% of their lost HP. This restoration effect can be triggered once every 10s and will not be affected by any Healing Bonus.
Aero DMG Bonus is increased by 15%.
Casting Mid-air Attack Cloudburst Dance increases Resonance Skill DMG Bonus by 15% for 5s.
The DMG Multiplier of Resonance Liberation Omega Storm is increased by 20%.
The DMG Multiplier of Resonance Skill Unbound Flow is increased by 30%.

Words.Title: Idle: II
Words.Content: This is a testament to my connection with the world around me, and it's very much my companion now, bearing witness to everything I've experienced on this journey.

Words.Title: Join Team: I
Words.Content: We still have a long journey ahead of us. Let's press on.

Words.Title: Join Team: III
Words.Content: Let me be there for everyone... As we head toward our shared future, leaving the past behind.

Words.Title: Ascension: I
Words.Content: The world around me... I can hear it clearer now.

Words.Title: Ascension: II
Words.Content: This power... it's mysterious, yet reassuring nonetheless.

Words.Title: Ascension: III
Words.Content: I still need more time to acquaint myself with this unfamiliar world.

Words.Title: Ascension: IV
Words.Content: A new journey awaits? Brimming with novel sounds, stories, and... fragmented memories.

Words.Title: Ascension: V
Words.Content: The place where the land ends is where the ocean begins. Our journey is far from ending.

DescList: Enhanced Mid-air Attack, Intro Skill, and Normal Attack recover Forte Gauge.
When Forte Gauge is full, Rover can cast enhanced Resonance Skill.

InputDetails.description: Mid-air Attack - Cloudburst Dance: Press when on the ground to leap into the air and then press .
Unbound Flow: When Forte Gauge is full, press .

Skyfall Severance: While in mid-air, press to remove all stacks of Spectro Frazzle, Havoc Bane, Fusion Burst, Glacio Chafe, and Electro Flare from the target hit and inflict 1 stack of Aero Erosion for each stack removed.
